<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - القيامة <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{فَيَوْمَئِذٍ وَقَعَتِ الْوَاقِعَةُ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
